
===========================
 LitterLens - RUN INSTRUCTIONS
===========================

You will need to open TWO(3 for email) TERMINAL WINDOWS to run the system:

----------------------------------------
TERMINAL 1 - Run the Python Backend (YOLO)
----------------------------------------
1. Open Command Prompt.
2. Navigate to the Python folder:
   cd C:\Users\ADMIN\Desktop\LitterLens\python
3. Run the backend app: 
   python app.py

   EX. C:\Users\ADMIN\Desktop\LitterLens\python> python app.py

----------------------------------------
TERMINAL 2 - Serve the Frontend Website
----------------------------------------
1. Open another Command Prompt.
2. Navigate to the root folder:
   cd C:\Users\ADMIN\Desktop\LitterLens
3. Start the web server:
   python -m http.server 8000

   EX. C:\Users\ADMIN\Desktop\LitterLens> python -m http.server 8000

----------------------------------------
OPEN YOUR BROWSER
----------------------------------------
Go to:
   C:\Users\ADMIN\Desktop\LitterLens OPEN THE HOMEPAGE.HTML

This will launch the LitterLens interface.
